abstract: The Volcker Rule’s biggest test may be just around the corner. | The Boies Schiller law firm is poised to pay year-end bonuses of as much as $300,000 to some of its associates. | House and Senate negotiators reached an agreement that amounts to a cease-fire in the budget wars.
